Physiotherapy

A significant proportion of those injured in accidents are known to benefit from physiotherapy services, which may include manual therapies, ultrasound and exercises.

Pegasus Medical have access to physiotherapists all over the UK.

Our team can arrange convenient, local physiotherapy sessions, directly with your client.

Our handy Pegasus Physiotherapy Cost Calculator can help you find details and costings for physiotherapists local to your client.

Simply enter the details related to a particular case into the boxes below and after clicking submit' you will then be able to download and print our quote.
